ed="T" n="0877c09"/><persName key="A013709">釋懷玉</persName>，姓<name>許</name>，<placeName key="PL000000003794">并州</placeName>人也。少而警利，日覽千<lb
ed="T" n="0877c10"/>言，早露鋒芒，逈<anchor xml:id="beg0877sgsz9"/>拔<anchor xml:id="end0877sgsz9"/>儕類。及其長也，戒節踰<lb
ed="T" n="0877c11"/>峻，<name>梵</name>場龜鑑<ptr target="#n1881"/>。志在修葺，無間彼此──<placeName key="PL000000003794">夏墟</placeName><ptr type="glossary" target="#g2127"/>寺<lb
ed="T" n="0877c12"/>宇，經有闕而必補，像有凋而遍修。三任紀<lb
ed="T" n="0877c13"/>綱，特有崇建。仍校讎大藏經二十餘本，祁<lb
ed="T" n="0877c14"/>寒<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2128"/>盛暑，不廢晨暮。增飾<placeName key="PL000000055043">淨土院</placeName>，興事任力<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2129"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0877c15"/>轉加殊麗。<persName key="A004379">代宗</persName>嘉<ref type="person" target="#A013709">之</ref>，委為<placeName key="PL000000055043">灌頂道場</placeName>主。真<lb
ed="T" n="0877c16"/>言祕訣有所在矣！春秋六十三，卒於<ref type="place" target="#PL000000055043">本院</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0877c17"/>云。</p>
